Package net.sourceforge.barcodegen.views.main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControllerMain
    ControllerMain is used to provide some seperation between ui and logic on MainFrame
    MainFrame
    Main dashboard for dealing with xml You can load an XML from the top bar Or you can load a whole folder of XMLs Display the list of orders.
    TableHandler
    Handles displaying the table on MainFrame receiving the selection of orders from user Takes its data from FileSession.fOrders Clicking on an order will select it by setting Order.setSelected(boolean) as true; Double clicking on a specifin order should launch the OrderDetail window
    TableModel  
    ViewHolder
    Holds all the view refences for MainFrame because there is a lot of them
